(2147, 1855, 'pre-alert_instructions:_air', 'SCAN OR  FAX US ALL DOCS RELATED TO THAT SHPT ( HAWB, MAWB, CARGO MANIFEST, COMMERCIAL INVOICE, PACKING LIST , CREDIT NOTE, DEBIT NOTE, ETC...) NOT LATER THAN 1 DAY BEFORE THE ARIVAL DATE.\r\nALL PRE-ALERTS OF SHIPMENTS TO VIET NAM ( HO CHI MINH , HAI PHONG , HA NOI ... ) MUST BE SENT TO OUR HEAD OFFICE IN HO CHI MINH CITY import1@ancshipping.com.vn , import2@ancshipping.com.vn or yang@ancshipping.com.vn '),
(2148, 1855, 'pre-alert_instructions:_ocean', 'SCAN OR  FAX US ALL DOCS RELATED TO THAT SHPT ( HBL, MBL, CARGO MANIFEST, CREDIT NOTE, DEBIT NOTE, ETC...) NOT LATER THAN 2 DAYS BEFORE THE ARIVAL DATE .ALL PRE-ALERTS OF SHIPMENTS TO VIET NAM ( HO CHI MINH , HAI PHONG , HA NOI ... ) MUST BE SENT TO OUR HEAD OFFICE IN HO CHI MINH CITY import1@ancshipping.com.vn , import2@ancshipping.com.vn or yang@ancshipping.com.vn '),
(2149, 1855, 'customs_clearance', 'ALL DOCS RELATED TO THAT SHPT (HOUSE BILL, MASTER BILL, SALES CONTRACT, COMMERCIAL INVOICE, PACKING LIST, HEALTH CERTIFICATE, CERTIFICATE OF ANALYSIS, C/O, ETC...) SHOULD BE SCANNED TO US FIRST AND LATER SENT ORIGINAL DOCS TO US .'),
(2150, 1855, 'transshipment_requirements', 'IF ANY REQUEST, PLS INFORM US IN PRE-ALERT.'),
(2151, 1855, 'legal_requirements_with_regards_to_commercial_invoices,_certificates_of_origin,_etc.', 'ALL DETAILS : SHIPPER\'S NAME , CONSIGNEE\'S NAME , DESCRIPTION OF GOODS , QUANTITY , GROSS WEIGHT, MEASUREMENT,... SHOWN ON HAWB , HB/L COMMERCIAL INVOICE , PACKING LIST , CERTIFICATE OF ORIGIN MUST BE THE SAME. ORIGINAL INVOICE , PACKING LIST ,... MUST BE SIGNED AND STAMPED.\r\n'),
(2152, 1855, 'dangerous_goods_requirements', 'MUST ASK FOR OUR CONFIRMATION BEFORE LOADING THE DG CARGO. PLS BE ADVISED THAT THERE WILL BE SOME ADDITIONAL CHARGES OCCURRED. ALSO PLS SHOW IT ON CARGO MANIFEST & HB/L OR HAWB'),
(2153, 1855, 'special_instructions', ' Pre-alert should  be sent to us at least 3 office hours  before the flight   arrive for air freight and 24 hours before ETA for sea freight   for manifest submiting .  Any adjustment or supplementary ( any document) after the flight / vessel  arrive will be against the amendment manifest of USD 95.00 per case  in Ho Chi Minh City & Ha Noi ;  220 USD per case in Cai Mep Terminal  ; 150 usd per case for Hai Phong , Da Nang shipment ; 250 usd  per case for Cai Lan shipment .\r\nWith Air shipment  please make sure all cartons have House Label . The fine for lack of House Label is 5 USD / Carton, min 45 USD / shipment  .\r\n\r\nALL FINE OCCURRED WILL BE INVOICED TO YOU.'),
