(4565, 1944, 'pre-alert_instructions:_air', 'Pre-Alerts should contain basic information such as:\r\nMAWB Number\r\nHAWB Number\r\nPieces and Weight\r\nShipper and Consignee\r\nFlight and arrival date\r\nCopy of AWB\r\nCopy of the invoice\r\nCopy of the manifest'),
(4566, 1944, 'pre-alert_instructions:_ocean', 'Pre-alert to reach us 2-3 days after vessel departure. Pre-alert to contain the following information:\r\nShipper/ Consignee (Including Tel/ Fax No and PIC)\r\nCommodity\r\nNumber of cartons\r\nWeight\r\nCBM\r\nVessel name\r\nContainer number or info LCL\r\nRelease agent (Shipping line)\r\nETD\r\nETA'),
(4567, 1944, 'customs_clearance', 'We can do Customs clearance for any air and ocean shipments if we have proper invoice and packing list, certificate of insurance is not essential. Duty and VAT has to be paid in advance if we do not know the customer. Customs clearance can be made only if shipment is consigned to a registered company/person in the relevant country. '),
