(4641, 1947, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_mawb', 'Master MAWB should be consigned to Enkay Express, showing freight terms: Pre-paid \r\nOriginal documents, namely Shipper Invoice and Packing List a must, for clearance.\r\nOther services required at Destination should be mentioned i.e. Customs Clearance/Delivery \r\n'),
(4642, 1947, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_mb/l', 'Master B/L should be consigned to Enkay Express, showing freight terms: Pre-paid \r\nOriginal documents, namely Shipper Invoice and Packing List a must, for clearance.\r\nOther services required at Destination should be mentioned i.e. Customs Clearance/Delivery '),
(4643, 1947, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_hawb', 'HAWB to be consigned to final receiver, showing freight terms, collect, details of amount \r\nOriginal Shipper\'s Invoice and packing list to accompany the shipment.\r\nPre-Alert should be sent to us as soon as the shipment is booked or MAWB has been prepared with all details. Copy of MAWB/HAWB/ should be faxed/emailed prior to shipment arrival. Airfreight shipment on Freight collect - Two sets of HAWB should be prepared. One set of \"\"AS AGREED\"\" for customs clearance purpose and Second set \"\"As per selling rate\"\" for consignee and both sets of HAWB must be sent with the MAWB. '),
(4644, 1947, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_hb/l', 'HB/L to be consigned to final receiver, showing freight terms, collect, details of amount \r\nOriginal Shipper Invoice and Packing list to accompany the shipment.\r\nPre-Alert should be sent to us once the shipment is booked or MBL has been made with all details. Copy of MBL/HBL should be faxed prior to shipment arrival. '),
(4645, 1947, 'pre-alert_instructions:_air', 'Always pre-alert to be received prior to shipment arrival, indicating AWB / flight details, ETA, number of packages, shipper consignee, DGR, special handling, if any.\r\nPre-Alert should be sent to us as soon as shipment is booked or MAWB has been prepared with all details. Copy of MAWB/HAWB/should be faxed immediately. For Airfreight shipments on Freight collect two sets of HAWB should be made. One set \"\"AS AGREED\"\" for customs clearance purpose and Second set \"\"As per selling rate\"\" for consignee and both sets of HAWB must be sent with the MAWB. \r\nOriginal shipper\'s invoice/packing list must be sent with the MAWB & HAWB.Shipment cannot be cleared in the absence of these documents.\r\n'),
(4646, 1947, 'pre-alert_instructions:_ocean', 'Always pre-alert to be received prior to shipment arrival, indicating B/L ,Vessel Details, ETA, number of packages, shipper consignee, DGR, special handling, if any.\r\nPre-Alert should be sent to us as soon as shipment booked or MBL has been made with all details. Copy of MBL/HBL should be faxed immediately. \r\nOriginal shipper\'s invoice/packing list must be sent with the MBL & HBL .Shipment cannot be cleared in the absence of these documents.'),
