(5846, 1988, 'special_instructions', ' Pre-alert should  be sent to us at least 3 office hours  before the flight   arrive for air freight and 24 hours before ETA for sea freight   for manifest submiting .  Any adjustment or supplementary ( any document) after the flight / vessel  arrive will be against the amendment manifest of USD 95.00 per case  in Ho Chi Minh City & Ha Noi ;  220 USD per case in Cai Mep Terminal  ; 150 usd per case for Hai Phong , Da Nang shipment ; 250 usd  per case for Cai Lan shipment .\r\nWith Air shipment  please make sure all cartons have House Label . The fine for lack of House Label is 5 USD / Carton, min 45 USD / shipment  .\r\n\r\nALL FINE OCCURRED WILL BE INVOICED TO YOU.'),
