(5858, 1989, 'how_to_consign_a_master_airwaybill', 'Back to Back shipment\r\n\r\nShipper HTFN member name and address at origin. \r\n\r\nConsignee to be addressed to (if destination is Jakarta) : \r\nPT. CARDIG Logistics Indonesia\r\nT.P.S Taman Soewarna Unit B 3\r\nSoekarno - Hatta International Airport\r\nCengkareng - Tangerang Indonesia\r\nTel. 62-21-559 116 20\r\nFax. 62.21.550.2127 \r\nAtt : Mr. Suryanto\r\n\r\nDeclared as \" Consolidated Shipment as per attached HAWB\" (or manifest if issued)\r\n\r\nFreight must be Prepaid only\r\n\r\nConsolidation Shipment\r\n\r\nShipper, Consignee (same as for back to back shipment)\r\n\r\nDeclare as \" Consolidated Shipment as per attached Manifest\"\r\n\r\nFreight must be prepaid only\r\n'),
(5859, 1989, 'how_to_consign_a_master_b/l', 'Back to Back shipment\r\n\r\nShipper HTFN member name and address at origin.\r\n\r\nConsignee to be addressed to (if destination is Jakarta) :\r\nPT. CARDIG LOGISTICS INDONESIA\r\nHalim Perdana Kusuma Airport\r\nJakarta 13610 - Indonesia\r\nTel. 62-21-8089 0040 - 41\r\nFax. 62.21.808.0048\r\nAtt : Mr. Iswan Izhar\r\n\r\nMark and Number as per shipping instruction and as put on boxes, etc.\r\n\r\nContainer and seal number in case of consolidated / loaded FCL - NVOCC B/L . Express Bill of Lading is recommended.\r\n\r\nFreight to be Prepaid only.\r\n\r\nConsolidation Shipment \r\n\r\nShipper , Consignee (same as back to back shipment) \r\nDeclaration : \" As per attached Statement \" \r\nContainer and seal number, type of container, weight and measurment etc. as normal procedure. \r\nAttached to master B/L a statement with container and seal number, type of container, weight of container, all each individual HB/L with full detail (Number of HB/L , Marks , number of packages , description of goods , weight , measurment) and total packages , weight. \r\nFreight to be prepaid. \r\n'),
(5860, 1989, 'how_to_consign_a_house_airwaybill', 'Never state \"AS AGREED\" to declare the freight. Customs will calculate the duties and taxes based on the higher rates, and they will use rates in MAWB or MBL that higher than the real freight cost.\r\n\r\nShipper, Consignee, etc as per shipping instruction / LC / Purchase order plus telephone number. \r\n\r\nFreight may as Prepaid or Collect, agreed amount of selling rate must be mentioned or confirm by destination agent.\r\n\r\nIn case of Coload Shipment / Consolidation where HAWB use as agent to agent shipping document, freight must be prepaid and the final importer shipping document may as collect. \r\n'),
(5861, 1989, 'how_to_consign_a_house_b/l', 'Never state \"AS AGREED\" to declare the freight. Customs will calculate the duties and taxes based on the higher rates, and they will use rates in MAWB or MBL that higher than the real freight cost.\r\n\r\nShipper, Consignee, etc. as per shipping instruction / LC / Purchase Order plus telepone number. \r\nFreight may as Prepaid or Collect. \r\nIf loaded into a FCL include Container and seal number. \r\n'),
(5862, 1989, 'creating_consolidation_manifest:_air', 'House Manifest form not specified, normal form can be used but please include the following:\r\n\r\nMAWB NUMBER \r\nHAWB NUMBER \r\nPIECES AND WEIGHT \r\nSHIPPER AND CONSIGNEE \r\nFLIGHT AND DEPARTURE DATE \r\nGOODS DESCRIPTION \r\nCOLLECT OR PREPAID \r\n'),
(5863, 1989, 'creating_consolidation_manifest:_ocean', 'Sea Cargo manifest where as form not specified, normal form can be use, include the following information:\r\n\r\nMB/L \r\nPort of Loading \r\nPort of Discharge \r\nConsolidator name \r\nDestination agent name (CARDIG LOGISTICS INDONESIA) \r\nVessel \r\nVoyage \r\nETS/ETA \r\nContainer and seal no. \r\nAll per individual HB/L number \r\nNumber and type of packages \r\nGross weight \r\nMeasurement \r\nDescription of goods \r\nShipper / consignee and notify party full address \r\nFreight prepaid or collect but not the freight amount itself \r\nShipping marks \r\nTotal of package, weight, measurement at the bottom \r\n\r\nThis manifest must be stamped and signed. \r\n'),
(5864, 1989, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_mawb', 'Master Final destination\r\nCargo under Back to Back and Consolidation can only be accepted with Master final destination Jakarta, Surabaya, Semarang and Denpasar where as CARDIG LOGISTICS has its international inbound traffic offices. For other destination within Indonesia, please consult CARDIG LOGISTICS Jakarta office prior shipping arrangement \r\n'),
(5865, 1989, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_mb/l', 'Master Final destination Cargo under Back to Back and Consolidation can only be accepted with Master final destination Jakarta, Surabaya, Semarang and Denpasar where as Cardig Logistics has its international inbound traffic offices. '),
