(7060, 2033, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_hawb', 'Always show the full description of goods, terms of shipment and the full charges pre-paid or collect. If possible please show the H.S. code used on exportation of the goods. '),
(7061, 2033, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_hb/l', 'Always show the full description of goods, terms of shipment and the full charges pre-paid or collect. If possible please show the H.S. code used on exportation of the goods. '),
(7062, 2033, 'pre-alert_instructions:_air', 'Always send both e-mail notification to airimp@jenkinson.ie and a full faxed pre-alert in advance of the shipment. Please include the following:\r\n\r\nMAWB number \r\nHAWB number \r\nManifest \r\nCommercial Invoice \r\nFlight and Arrival Date \r\nplus any other supporting formal documents ( EUR\'s/Cert A/GSP forms,etc) '),
(7063, 2033, 'pre-alert_instructions:_ocean', 'Always send both e-mail notification to seaimports@jenkinson.ie and a full faxed pre-alert in advance of the shipment. We require a copies of the following: \r\nMB/L number - send the e-mail to \r\nHB/L number \r\nCommercial Invoice \r\nManifest \r\nAgent\'s Invoice \r\nplus any other supporting formal documents ( EUR\'s/Cert A/GSP forms,etc) '),
(7064, 2033, 'customs_clearance', 'No - clearance requires specific permissions from the consignee, therefore early notification allows us to obtain permission or instruct our HTFN partner on a course of action. \r\nPermission from the consignee is required to use their duty payment account(s) ( referred to as TAN accounts). Therefore the earlier we know about the shipment the more likely it is that we will obtain clearance permission, thus future shipments '),
(7065, 2033, 'transshipment_requirements', 'Goods which are for transshipment internally or externally must do so under bond, we therefore require the earliest possible notification, along with the ultimate consignees full address and customs related details. '),
(7066, 2033, 'legal_requirements_with_regards_to_commercial_invoices,_certificates_of_origin,_etc.', 'Commercial invoices, certificates, etc are legally required to show the proper name, address, description of goods, value of goods and shipping terms ( CIF etc and applicable charges) '),
(7067, 2033, 'dangerous_goods_requirements', 'AIR:\r\nWe require to be pre-alerted with copies of the dangerous goods declaration (DGR), along with full contact details, in order to book vehicle and delivery as per DGR regulations. \r\n\r\nOCEAN:\r\nWe require to be pre-alerted with copies of the dangerous goods term card, along with full contact details, in order to book vehicle and delivery as per DGR regulations. Also MDSS ( Material Data Safety Sheets) '),
(7068, 2033, 'special_instructions', 'When sending the first pre-alert e-mail to any Jenkinson Logistics office always copy the HTFNTEAM @jenkinson.IE . Secondly check the appropriate office(s) to notify. If it is an ocean consignment also notify : seaimports@jenkinson.ie '),
