(7976, 2067, 'how_to_consign_a_house_airwaybill', '- Cnee\'s name and address.\r\n- Phone number, email and contact person. \r\n- Importer\'s CUIT (vat) number (in \"cnee\'s name & address\").\r\n\r\n\r\nRemarks: otherwise customs penalties will be charged.'),
