(8262, 2077, 'legal_requirements_with_regards_to_commercial_invoices,_certificates_of_origin,_etc.', 'Commercial Invoice needs to contain: \r\n- supplier/buyer\r\n- country of origin\r\n- shipping terms (should match on the AWB)\r\n- payment terms\r\n- unit/total price\r\n- description of goods\r\n- currency\r\n- invoice date & No.\r\n- the invoice should state \"commercial invoice\" \r\n\r\nProforma Invoice should contain same  criteria for commercial invoice, except payment terms. In this case it should state:\r\n- value for customs purposes only\r\n- if samples: \"sample\"'),
