(8304, 2079, 'how_to_consign_a_master_b/l', 'The Master Bill of Lading should mention all the following details\r\n. SHIPPER\'S NAME & ADDRESS\r\n. CONSIGNEE\'S NAME & ADDRESS TO READ AS:\r\nEnkay Express LLC\r\nP.O Box#55393\r\nDubai, UAE\r\nTel:  +971 (4) 7034777\r\nFax:  +971 (4) 2834361\r\n. NOTIFY PARTY\'S : SAME AS CONSIGNEE\r\n. BILL OF LADING#\r\n. M/VESSEL NAME & VOYAGE NO.\r\n. PORT OF LOADING\r\n. MARKS & NUMBERS\r\n. CONTAINER & SEAL NUMBER\r\n. NUMBER & KIND OF PACKAGES\r\n. DESCRIPTION OF GOODS\r\n. GROSS WEIGHT\r\n. TARE WEIGHT\r\n. MEASUREMENT (CBM)\r\n. FREIGHT PRE PAID\r\n. PLACE & DATE OF ISSUE\r\nAll the documents related to the shipment should match each other in all respect viz. No: of packages, Gross Weight & measurement. '),
(8305, 2079, 'how_to_consign_a_house_b/l', 'All Original Documents should be received 72 hours prior to vessel arrival at designated port in Dubai.\r\nFor L/C\'s we should have full set of copies by fax, 72 hrs prior to vessel arrival.\r\n1. In case of L/C, pls. specify Bank\'s full name\r\n2. In case of COD(Cash on delivery), pls. mention your instructions for COD shipment clearly in the house mentioning the amount & currency to be collected.\r\n3. In case of CAD(Cash against delivery) through Bank,Pls. mention clear instructions for freight & other charges to be collected from final consignee.\r\n*The House Bill of Lading, should mention the following details.\r\n. EXPORTERS / SUPPLIERS COMPLETE NAME & ADDRESS\r\n. FINAL CONSIGNEE\'S NAME & ADDRESS\r\n. OTHER DETAILS SAME AS IN M B/L'),
(8306, 2079, 'creating_consolidation_manifest:_air', 'The Cargo Manifest in general should mention the following information: \r\nFROM : \r\nTO : \r\nMAWB #\r\nAirline\r\nFlight # and Dtd\r\nDeparture Airport\r\nArrival Airport\r\nDate \r\nFile Ref # \r\n_____________________________________________________________________ HAWB #, Shipper, C/nee, Destination, Pgks, G.Wt, Goods, CC \r\nIn case of Consolidation manifest the HAWB # will continue so far as how much so every shipments you have. '),
(8307, 2079, 'creating_consolidation_manifest:_ocean', 'The Cargo Manifest in general should mention the following information: \r\nFROM \r\nTO \r\nB/L No. \r\nVESSEL NAME \r\nCONTAINER No.\r\nETD \r\nETA \r\nH B/L No. , SHIPPER , CONSIGNEE, GROSS WEIGHT, VOLUME, PKG., TYPE, COMMODITY, MARKS, FREIGHT PREPAID/ COLLECT.'),
(8308, 2079, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_mawb', 'Master MAWB should be consigned to Enkay Express, showing freight terms: pre-paid \r\nOriginal documents, namely Invoice, packing list and COO a must, for clearance.'),
(8309, 2079, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_mb/l', 'Master B/L should be consigned to Enkay Express, showing freight terms: pre-paid \r\nOriginal documents, namely Invoice, packing list and COO a must, for clearance.'),
(8310, 2079, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_hawb', 'HAWB to be consigned to final receiver, showing freight terms, collect, details of amount \r\nCopy of Invoice, packing list and COO to accompany the shipment.'),
(8311, 2079, 'instructions_for_issuance_of_a_hb/l', 'HB/L to be consigned to final receiver, showing freight terms, collect, details of amount \r\nCopy of Invoice, packing list and COO to accompany the shipment.'),
(8312, 2079, 'pre-alert_instructions:_air', 'Always pre-alert to be received prior to shipment arrival, indicating B/L or AWB / flight details, ETA, number of packages, shipper consignee, DGR, special handling, if any.\r\nPre-Alert should be advised prior to the shipment along with a copy of MAWB & HAWB for the following reasons : \r\n1. To check whether the shipment has been consigned as per the above instructions and if not to revert back to the agent 2. Pre-Alert is required for insurance purpose prior to shipment arrival. '),
(8313, 2079, 'pre-alert_instructions:_ocean', 'Always pre-alert to be received prior to shipment arrival, indicating B/L or AWB / flight details, ETA, number of packages, shipper consignee, DGR, special handling, if any.\r\nPre-Alert should be advised prior to the shipment along with a copy of MB/L & H B/L for the following reasons: \r\n1. To check whether the shipment has been consigned as per the above instructions or not to revert back to the agent.\r\n2. Pre-Alert is required for insurance purpose prior to shipment arrival.'),
(8314, 2079, 'transshipment_requirements', ''),
(8315, 2079, 'legal_requirements_with_regards_to_commercial_invoices,_certificates_of_origin,_etc.', 'AIR:\r\nCertificate of Origin (need to be attested from the chamber of commerce or legalised from the Kuwaiti Consulate) as per the agreement between the c/nee and the supplier. \r\nCommercial Invoice (need to be attested from the chamber of commerce or legalised from the Kuwaiti Consulate) as per the agreement between the c/nee and the supplier. The Invoice should mention the Currency of value mentioned. \r\nPacking list \r\nOCEAN:\r\nC/O should show manufacturer\'s name & address & country of origin. ( needs to be attested from the Chamber Of Commerce or legalized from the Kuwait Consulate) \r\nIncase of L/C , it shall be authenticated from Kuwaiti Consulate. \r\nCommercial invoice ( needs to be attested from the Chamber Of Commerce )\r\nThe invoice should mention the following:\r\n- Currency of Value \r\n- Gross Weight\r\n- Net weight\r\n- No. of packages (it should tally with M B/L)\r\n- Unit Price and total Value\r\nPacking List '),
