(8525, 2087, 'how_to_consign_a_master_b/l', 'Please see the Shipping Instructions for the local Cargo Brokers office for exact details.  Generally, MB/L should be consigned to Cargo Brokers International, showing local address with telephone and fax number.  '),
(8526, 2087, 'how_to_consign_a_house_airwaybill', 'House Bills should be consigned from actual shipper to actual consignee.  \r\nIf shipment is being delivered to a third party, consignee should be the US Buyer, and the delivery address should be shown in the Handling or Accounting Information fields.    \r\nPlease ensure a complete address is used for the consignee.  \r\n'),
(8527, 2087, 'how_to_consign_a_house_b/l', 'House Bills should be consigned from actual shipper to actual consignee, with the US Broker/forwarder listed as a notify party. \r\nIf shipment is being delivered to a third party, consignee should be the US Buyer, and the delivery address should be shown as such on the HB/L. \r\nPlease ensure a complete address is used for the consignee.   \r\n'),
