(8982, 2103, 'special_instructions', 'IMPORTANT NOTE (AIR EXPORTS FROM USA):\r\nNew security regulations make distinctions between known and unknown shippers. Shipments from unknown shippers ( essentially new clients to Cargo Brokers ) are subject to special scrutiny which may delay the air routing by 4 or more days. \r\nWhen issuing an urgent routing order to Cargo Brokers, please verify with us if your routing may be subject to such delays so that you may advise your importer accordingly of the options available.\r\nTo help avoid potential delays, please provide the pick-up address of the shipment as early as possible so that we can accurately verify the known/unknown status of the shipper.  \r\n\r\n*Note these regulations apply to all US Freight Forwarders.  '),
