(8994, 2104, 'how_to_consign_a_master_airwaybill', 'For shipments to North Carolina and South Carolina (CLT, RDU, GSP) please consign MAWB to:\r\nCargo Brokers International, Inc.\r\n1512 Cross Beam Drive\r\nCharlotte, NC 28217 United States\r\nTel:  +1 (704) 357-3079 / Fax:  +1 (704) 357-1482'),
