(10, 1, '2018-02-26 19:06:57', '2018-02-26 19:06:57', 'SERVICE\n<img src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/d481b5_939374d58e364c6f964828acb2dd2d1f_mv2_d_5834_5834_s_4_2.png\" alt=\"\"/>\nRecognized as leaders in their respective markets, HTFN companies have built their reputations by offering the best possible service at the best possible price.EXPERTISE\n<img src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_9b0a9164d92b47899805e7f01ec42d25_mv2_d_1668_1576_s_2.png\" />\nLocal HTFN agents are ideally positioned to guide shippers through the intricacies of business by understanding local regulations as well as speaking the local language.FLEXIBILITY\n<img src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_1079c1d75c95476a94fb92ec5d86ec58_mv2_d_5834_5834_s_4_2.png\"/>\nHTFN offers a wide range of transportation and logistics programs tailored to meet your shipping needs. HTFNs independently operated agents offer a wide range of transportation and logistics programs, tailored to meet all customer needs.COVERAGE\n<img src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_d29a8cff5225472ca702f8c4d3d2e709_mv2_d_1820_2078_s_2.png\" />\nHTFN has carefully built a global network of reputable agents strategically located to manage shipments to virtually any destination worldwide.\nThe HTFN network spans the globe with more than 220 offices, employing over 6,000 staff and handling in excess of 2 million tons of cargo annually.		\n			<h1>GLOBAL REACH</h1>		\n		<p>HTFN is a unique global alliance that combines the capabilities of a multinational forwarder with the personal services of locally owned and operated agent companies.</p><p>Companies around the globe rely on HFTN\'s highly regarded reliable independent forwarding agents to provide essential freight transportation and logistical services.</p><p>The best of both worlds......Worldwide.</p>		\n			<h1>LOCAL TOUCH</h1>		\n		<p>As one of the leading of global multimodal forwarding services, HTFN provides clients with a comprehensive range of freight managed services tailored to meet their individual needs.</p><p>Recognized as leaders in their respective markets, HTFN member companies have built their reputations by offering the best possible service at the best possible price.</p>		\n					<figure>\n		<img width=\"458\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_dde33e22e7d842a89bf6a9dc40db9719_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_dde33e22e7d842a89bf6a9dc40db9719_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2.png 458w, http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_dde33e22e7d842a89bf6a9dc40db9719_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2-300x240.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 458px) 100vw, 458px\" />				<figcaption>AIR FREIGHT</figcaption>\n					</figure>\n					<figure>\n		<img width=\"452\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_a7f51eb109f543c3b45c08ca696ac851_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_a7f51eb109f543c3b45c08ca696ac851_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2.png 452w, http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_a7f51eb109f543c3b45c08ca696ac851_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2-300x244.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\" />				<figcaption>OCEAN FREIGHT</figcaption>\n					</figure>\n		<h1>TRANSPORTATION\nPRODUCTS</h1>\nAIR FREIGHT\n<p>HTFN negotiates the lowest available rates with all carriers and charter operators.</p>\nOCEAN FREIGHT\n<p>HTFN offers a full range of maritime services.</p>		\n					<figure>\n		<img width=\"453\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_6d3e72b5ad9b4ccab46f2684e9451104_mv2_d_1210_1209_s_2.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_6d3e72b5ad9b4ccab46f2684e9451104_mv2_d_1210_1209_s_2.png 453w, http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_6d3e72b5ad9b4ccab46f2684e9451104_mv2_d_1210_1209_s_2-300x243.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 453px) 100vw, 453px\" />				<figcaption>RAIL</figcaption>\n					</figure>\n					<figure>\n		<img width=\"453\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_110b868b5bb0424aab0cb7237a868fd6_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_110b868b5bb0424aab0cb7237a868fd6_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2.png 453w, http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d481b5_110b868b5bb0424aab0cb7237a868fd6_mv2_d_1200_1200_s_2-300x243.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 453px) 100vw, 453px\" />				<figcaption>ROAD</figcaption>\n					</figure>\n		ROAD &\n RAIL\n<p>Full truckload (FTL) and less than truckload (LTL) on global basis and rail services, where and when available.</p>\nIMPORTS & EXPORTS\n<p>Customs brokerage and import clearances are performed by local agents that know the language and local regulations.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\">\n						READ MORE\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"#\">\n						CONTACT US\n					</a>\n		<h1>VERTICAL MARKET SUPPORT</h1>\nFREIGHT MANAGEMENT SERVICES\n<p>HTFN is the one of the world\'s leading providers of global multi-modal forwarding services providing clients with a comprehensive range of freight-managed services.</p>\nCONTRACT LOGISTICS\n<p>HTFN provides clients across the globe with a comprehensive range of contract logistics services.</p>SPECIALIST SERVICES\n<p>We are specialists in a range of services covering all aspects of industrial vertical market segments.</p>\nCONSULTANCY\n<p>HTFN\'s experts listen to you in your language, in your market, in your business to develop a solution as unique as the requirement.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\">\n						READ MORE\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"#\">\n						CONTACT US\n					</a>', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2018-03-04 01:36:38', '2018-03-04 01:36:38', '', 0, 'http://dev.htfn.com/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
