(421, 1, '2018-03-15 17:18:25', '2018-03-15 17:18:25', 'The following message was read out by the Board of Directors to all attending HTFN conference attendees in Dublin on the 23rd of May:\r\n\r\n\"<strong>Dear HTFN Friends,</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>You would have heard by now about the suicide bombing in Manchester last night, which so far resulted in the death of 22 people.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>We at HTFN are the perfect example to show our staff, families and friends ... and indeed the rest of the world ... that, regardless of the colour of our skin, different religions or political beliefs ...</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>WE ARE FAMILY!</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Let us keep our hearts open and carry this message back home.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>And let us STAND UP to have one minute of silence in respect of the dead, as well as for the physically and mentally injured.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>THANK YOU</strong>\"', 'Message from Board', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'message-from-board', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:18:25', '2018-03-15 17:18:25', '', 0, 'http://dev.htfn.com/?p=421', 0, 'post', '', 0),
