(433, 1, '2018-03-15 18:57:25', '2018-03-15 18:57:25', '<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-431 alignleft\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/LG-project-5-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" />HTFN Poland, ADECON, recently handled their largest cargo project in their company history, breaking their own record! Production line equipment delivered to a new factory, LG Chem Energy for the production of vehicle batteries made this project an interesting challenge for ADECON.\r\n\r\nConsisting of 137 cargo containers, all special project equipment such as open tops and flat racks was out of gauge or oversized. The expert staff of ADECON was able to take possession of the cargo at the Port of Bremerhaven and efficiently handle the unloading, stripping, lashing, Customs documentation inspections and lowbed trailer deliveries smoothly and on time to their customer in Wroclaw, Poland.\r\n\r\nIn addition to breaking their own record, ADECON had great cause for excitement for the past few months in 2017.<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-432 alignright\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/adeconnstage2aa-300x158.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"158\" />\r\n\r\nThe celebration of their 10th Anniversary was the big event with a huge banquet party with almost 150 staff, friends, customers, vendors in attendance. The ADECON celebrated their growth from a container trucking company with 2 trucks to an experienced forwarding operation with a fleet of 50 plus units, sea-air and project cargo departments, dangerous good warehouse, container depot, and additional office locations.\r\n\r\nADECON continued to celebrate their growth by exhibiting at the European Transport Logistic Fair in Munich , Germany, showing the logistics world it was proud of its accomplishments at the largest fair in the industry. With a large exhibit booth and 3 ADECON Team members they received positive feedback and are already making plans to attend the 2019 Fair.\r\n\r\nCongratulations ADECON Poland for this record breaking success and your 10 years of exceptional growth!', 'HTFN Poland Breaks Own Record!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '430-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:57:25', '2018-03-15 18:57:25', '', 430, 'http://dev.htfn.com/430-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
