(441, 1, '2018-03-15 19:17:31', '2018-03-15 19:17:31', 'HTFN Missouri, RAM International, considers \"Here We Grow Again\" an understatement as they literally triple the size of their facility by moving soon into a new warehouse location of 32,000 square feet!\r\n\r\nIn their current location in St. Louis they presently house their operations in 10,000 square feet and are looking forward to the \"triple threat\" by tripling their size! This will be a combination of more warehouse space as well as a full three line crating operation. Their services include packing everything from small works of art with values of a quarter million dollars to multi-million dollar machinery with the biggest piece at over 100,000 lbs. Another excellent feature of this warehouse will be the cold storage operations with three different cold rooms, with varying temperature for excellent cold chain solutions for their customers in the Pharma and Ag-Science areas.\r\n\r\nRAM, a C-TPAT approved forwarder has an experienced team that has built their reputation on handling oversized specialized airfreight, Haz-MAT cargo, a broad range of passive and active temperature-controlled cargo, and the very latest in e-commerce technology. RAM International employees are looking forward to this growth and their progress into the future. Congratulations RAM International on this outstanding growth achievement!', 'HTFN Missouri USA To Become A Triple Threat!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'htfn-missouri-usa-to-become-a-triple-threat', '', '', '2018-03-15 19:17:31', '2018-03-15 19:17:31', '', 0, 'http://dev.htfn.com/?p=441', 0, 'post', '', 0),
