(447, 1, '2018-03-15 19:37:44', '2018-03-15 19:37:44', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-448\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Colbeck-Logo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"267\" height=\"84\" />\r\n<h3>COLEBECK &amp; CLARKE Inc. - CANADA</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.colbeck-clarke.com/\" target=\"_whole\">www.colbeck-clarke.com</a>\r\n\r\nFounded in 1997, Colbeck &amp; Clarke Inc. is Canadas premier logistics management company with offices in Toronto and Montreal.\r\n\r\nWe offer a full-range of freight forwarding and total logistic management services suited to meet your specific needs all over Canada. We understand that each client has their own specific requirements. Being able to adapt to these requirements is what makes us industry leaders.\r\n\r\nWe believe strongly in working with our clients and consider ourselves a service partner rather than a service provider. Our team is prepared to work with you to determine the best solution to all your international freight needs.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-449\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Kompas-300x91.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"91\" />\r\n<h3>KOMPAS INTERNATIONAL TRANSPORT</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.kompastransport.com/\" target=\"_whole\">www.kompastransport.com</a>\r\n\r\nKompas International Transport Company Ltd. was founded in Serbia in1994. The basic activities of our company are the business of international freight forwarding and international transportation services.\r\n\r\nKompas is an international freight forwarder of goods. We operate on the international market in road transport since our founding in 1994. Also, since the foundation of our company, we nurture and invest in our reputation with providing competitive services, building a loyal local and international clients, providing safe and quality service and complete geographical coverage of their presence in the whole EU territory. Because of logistics services we provide, and thanks to many years of experience in working in the international market we have gained good reputation among our clients\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-450\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FEI.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"160\" height=\"76\" />\r\n<h3>FEI CARGO LIMITED</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.feicargo.com/\" target=\"_whole\">www.feicargo.com</a>\r\n\r\nWith more than two decades experience in providing responsive and customized solutions, FEI is a global reflection of what a freight forwarder ought to be. And thanks to the vision and dynamism of its founder Mr. Pratap Nair, FEI is today, an internationally-acclaimed logistics group - at par with the best in the business and a leader in terms of cost-effectiveness.\r\n\r\nWith its corporate office situated in Mumbai, FEI enjoys an impressive clientele, serviced and supported from twenty offices across the country. Multi-location, multi-faceted and backed by a strong cohesive team of more than 300 experts, FEI is on a mission to provide excellence and value-addition to its customers.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-454\" src=\"http://dev.htfn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/PRIMY-logo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"160\" height=\"121\" />\r\n\r\nPRIMARY OCEAN AIR LOGISTICS CO., LTD\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.primyair.com/\" target=\"_whole\">www.primyair.com</a>\r\n\r\nPrimy Ocean Air Logistics Co. Ltd. is a Shanghai based international freight forwarding established in 2006. It has set up branches in Ningbo, Qingdao, Tianjin, Beijing, Xiamen, Shenzhen and Hong Kong with a team of enthusiastic, skillful and well-experienced staff to solve the needs of their clients in a quick, reliable and cost effective manner.\r\n\r\nPrimy specializes in logistics and international freight forwarding with IATA and FMC licensed, provides air, sea, logistics solutions and ground transportation within a well-structured supply chain.\r\n\r\nWe run our own warehouses in Shanghai and Hong Kong to provide tailor-made logistics services and warehouse management system. Being the ISO tanks owner and operator, Primy is also specialized in handling the ISO tanks and dangerous goods.\r\n\r\nPrimy is financially sound and has installed the de-facto industry software programmes for the freight industry to ensure compatibility with clients.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Meet our newest HTFN Members!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'meet-our-newest-htfn-members', '', '', '2018-03-15 19:51:33', '2018-03-15 19:51:33', '', 0, 'http://dev.htfn.com/?p=447', 0, 'post', '', 0),
